          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="journey-item reveal">
        <div class="journey-year">2022</div>
        <div class="journey-story">
          <h3>‚òÅÔ∏è Into the Cloud</h3>
          <p>
            Began DevOps at Orisha Healthcare. Reliable infrastructure in healthcare 
